Containers are lightweight virtualization technology used to package applications and their dependencies together.

Goals
-Faster deployment
-Continuous Integration & Deployment
-Automation
-Collaboration between teams

Key Practices
-CI/CD
-Containerization
-Monitoring
-Infrastructure as Code
Advantages:
- Portability
- Isolation
- Faster deployment
- Efficient resource usage

Examples:
Docker
Kubernetes
Podman
